OL,3,CCouple who lost their child on holiday
OL,4,Coffer warnings to other teenagers
OL,6,FThat feeling of devastation is one
OL,7,Fwhich John Channon, from Rhoose in the
OL,8,FVale of Glamorgan, is all too familiar
OL,9,Fwith.
OL,11,FJohn's son Tom died six year ago,
OL,12,Fafter falling while trying to make his
OL,13,Fway back to his hotel in in Magaluf.
OL,15,FThis time of year is a difficult one
OL,16,Ffor John and his family, especially
OL,17,Fwhen similar incidents are still
OL,18,Fhappening.
