OL,3,CCouple who lost their child on holiday
OL,4,Coffer warnings to other teenagers
OL,6,FJohn said: "Obviously we've been on
OL,7,Ffamily holidays before but naturally
OL,8,Fas a parent you do worry.
OL,10,F"We try to do everything that we could
OL,11,Fto make sure the kids will be safe.
OL,13,F"But unfortunately people aren't going
OL,14,Fto be looking out for you and you
OL,15,Freally have to do a lot yourself."
OL,17,FHe adds: "I think it really fills us
OL,18,Fwith sadness because you feel after
OL,19,Fwhat happened to us, it shouldn't
OL,20,Fhappening again.
