OL,3,CCouple who lost their child on holiday
OL,4,Coffer warnings to other teenagers
OL,6,F"It's something that you have to find
OL,7,Fa way through and partly the way
OL,8,Fthrough for us was to try and find
OL,9,Fsomething positive to come out of
OL,10,Fthis."
OL,12,FThat has come in the form of a safety
OL,13,Fcampaign in Tom's name, one developed
OL,14,Fwith his former school and shared with
OL,15,Fschools and colleges right across
OL,16,FWales.
OL,18,FJohn adds: "It will make other people
OL,19,Faware of potential dangers and hazards
OL,20,Fand maybe make them better prepared
OL,21,Fand plan better."
