OL,3,CCouple who lost their child on holiday
OL,4,Coffer warnings to other teenagers
OL,6,FFor John, the safety of future young
OL,7,Ftravellers is what Tom's legacy is all
OL,8,Fabout.
OL,10,FBut what can be done to minimise the
OL,11,Frisk?
OL,13,FSuzanne Cumpston is a travel agent
OL,14,Ffrom Sam Smith Travel. She said: "Make
OL,15,Fsure that you take a very good
OL,16,Finsurance policy out. Make sure that
OL,17,Fyou have a 24-hour emergency telephone
OL,18,Fnumber on that policy, and also to
OL,19,Fgive that telephone number to their
OL,20,Fparents and guardians back to the UK."
